<h2>Real Test: Same Prompt, Three Results</h2>
<p>To give you a real sense of how these AIs compare, here are tests using the same prompt across all three platforms.</p>

<h3>Test 1: Writing — Startup Landing Page Copy</h3>
<p><strong>Prompt:</strong> "Write a compelling hero section for a startup landing page. The product is an AI-powered social media scheduler. Tone: professional but approachable. Keep it under 100 words."</p>

<table>
<thead><tr><th>AI</th><th>Result</th><th>Verdict</th></tr></thead>
