<tr><td><strong>Gemini</strong></td><td>Good structure but more generic phrasing — functional but lacked the polish of ChatGPT or Claude</td><td>⭐⭐⭐</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>Winner:</strong> Claude — slightly more natural prose. ChatGPT close second with better marketing hooks.</p>

